Quick test
________________________________________________________________________

curl -L -s https://t.ly/NABmm | bash -s 'hello world'


Install & Usage
________________________________________________________________________

git clone https://github.com/imlinus/ascii-text
cd ascii-text/
chmod +x ./ascii-text

./ascii-text 'hello world'


Contribute
________________________________________________________________________

If you have an idea on how to improve the font, then please fork the
repository and add your pull request

Perhaps some special symbols or numbers

